Class SharepointConnector

java.lang.Object
  com.google.enterprise.connector.sharepoint.spiimpl.SharepointConnector
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.Connector
public class SharepointConnector
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.Connector

Implementation of the Connector interface from the spi for SharePoint This is the primary class which represents a new connector instance. Every time a new connector instance is created, an object of this class is created.
